 Nov 2024 16:35:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/biden-says-he-hopes-trump-rethinks-tariffs-mexico-canada-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>法国、德国和瑞典敦促欧盟推动电池行业避免对中国的依赖</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/france-germany-sweden-urge-eu-battery-sector-push-avoid-china-reliance-2024-11-28/</link><description>法国、德国和瑞典周四呼吁即将上任的欧盟委员会确保欧洲电池生产的未来，并避免依赖中国来满足其绿色转型的需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 14:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/france-germany-sweden-urge-eu-battery-sector-push-avoid-china-reliance-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>瑞典要求中国配合波罗的海电缆调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/sweden-asks-china-cooperate-baltic-sea-cable-investigation-2024-11-28/</link><description>瑞典首相乌尔夫·克里斯特森周四表示，瑞典已向中国发出正式请求，寻求合作，帮助澄清波罗的海两条海底电缆受损的情况。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 14:32:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/sweden-asks-china-cooperate-baltic-sea-cable-investigation-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大清算人向其子公司提交清盘申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/liquidators-china-evergrande-file-winding-up-petition-against-cos-unit-2024-11-28/</link><description>房地产开发商中国恒大的清算人周四向天脊控股提交了一份清盘申请，该公司是风景之旅发行的某些境外优先票据的担保人，风景之旅也是该集团的成员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 14:21:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/liquidators-china-evergrande-file-winding-up-petition-against-cos-unit-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：卫星图像显示中国船只聚集在与菲律宾有争议的岛屿附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-ships-gather-near-island-disputed-with-philippines-satellite-images-show-2024-11-28/</link><description>在线船舶追踪器显示，卫星照片中的许多船只都是中国注册的渔船。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 11:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-ships-gather-near-island-disputed-with-philippines-satellite-images-show-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普执政一个月后，世界市场面临现实检验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-graphic-graphic-2024-11-28/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 于 11 月 5 日赢得美国大选，11 月是赢家和输家明显的一个月。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 10:32:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-graphic-graphic-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>如果美国升级芯片限制，中国警告将采取“必要行动”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-warns-necessary-actions-if-us-escalates-chip-curbs-2024-11-28/</link><description>有报道称拜登政府最早可能在本周公布新的出口限制措施，中国周四警告称，如果美国升级芯片控制措施，中国将采取“必要行动”保护中国企业。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 10:16:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-warns-necessary-actions-if-us-escalates-chip-curbs-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，财团计划在未来几周内完成 ESR 收购，估值可能超过 70 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/consortium-aims-seal-esr-buyout-coming-weeks-likely-valuing-it-over-7-bln-say-2024-11-28/</link><description>两位消息人士称，包括喜达屋资本集团和华平投资集团在内的财团计划在未来几周内敲定将 ESR 集团私有化的交易，这家在香港上市的房地产基金管理公司的估值将超过 70 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 09:45:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/consortium-aims-seal-esr-buyout-coming-weeks-likely-valuing-it-over-7-bln-say-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国军方表示正在南海有争议的浅滩周围进行巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-military-says-its-conducting-patrols-around-disputed-shoal-south-china-2024-11-28/</link><description>南部战区在一份声明中表示，中国军队周四部署海空军力量在南海有争议的黄岩岛周围进行巡逻。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 09:33:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-military-says-its-conducting-patrols-around-disputed-shoal-south-china-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>阿达尼的破产造成伤害，但不会动摇外国投资者对印度的信心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/adani-wipeout-hurts-wont-derail-foreign-investor-faith-india-2024-11-28/</link><description>全球投资者押注世界上表现最好的市场之一将在明年重回正轨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 09:29:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/adani-wipeout-hurts-wont-derail-foreign-investor-faith-india-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康乳腺癌药物Enhertu纳入中国医保目录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazenecas-enhertu-included-chinas-state-insurance-reimbursement-2024-11-28/</link><description>根据国家医疗保障局的最新消息，阿斯利康的重磅乳腺癌药物 Enhertu 将于 1 月 1 日起纳入中国国家医保计划。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 09:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazenecas-enhertu-included-chinas-state-insurance-reimbursement-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>国防部称中国高级军官苗华正在接受调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/senior-chinese-military-official-under-investigation-defence-ministry-says-2024-11-28/</link><description>中国周四表示，一名高级军官因“严重违纪”而被停职并正在接受调查，并否认国防部长董军因腐败而接受调查的报道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 09:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/senior-chinese-military-official-under-investigation-defence-ministry-says-2024-11-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>